SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781067873
OL,3,CPoorest families must spend 85% of
OL,4,Cdisposable income to get healthy diet
OL,5,C` study
OL,7,FThe study found households in the
OL,8,Flowest income fifth of the UK
OL,9,Fpopulation would need to spend 49% of
OL,10,Ftheir disposable income to afford the
OL,11,FGovernment-recommended healthy diet,
OL,12,Fknown as the Eatwell Guide ` up four
OL,13,Fpercentage points since 2024.
OL,15,FThis increases to 85% of disposable
OL,16,Fincome for households with children `
OL,17,Fa 15 percentage point increase since
OL,18,F2024.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
