CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781067873
OL,3,CPoorest families must spend 85% of
OL,4,Cdisposable income to get healthy diet
OL,5,C` study
OL,7,FThe data was gathered last year before
OL,8,Fthe Middle East conflict broke out,
OL,9,Fmeaning families are set to be under
OL,10,Fincreasing pressure to afford food
OL,11,Fover the coming months.
OL,13,FJust one in 10 of those aged 11 to 18
OL,14,Feat five portions of fruit and
OL,15,Fvegetables a day while 95% consume
OL,16,Fmore than the recommended amount of
OL,17,Ffree sugar, according to the National
OL,18,FDiet and Nutrition Survey.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
