CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781067873
OL,3,CPoorest families must spend 85% of
OL,4,Cdisposable income to get healthy diet
OL,5,C` study
OL,7,FThe Food Foundation is calling for
OL,8,Furgent action, including mandatory
OL,9,Freporting by businesses of healthy
OL,10,Ffood sales, a support package for low-
OL,11,Fincome families to afford healthy and
OL,12,Fsustainable food, including an
OL,13,Fexpansion of Healthy Start, and a Good
OL,14,FFood Bill to provide long-term
OL,15,F"nutritional security and protection"
OL,16,Ffor consumers and farmers.
OL,26,@wD@AOUwD@eO]
