OL,3,CPoorest families must spend 85% of
OL,4,Cdisposable income to get healthy diet
OL,5,C` study
OL,7,FFood Foundation executive director
OL,8,FAnna Taylor said: "The Broken Plate
OL,9,Freport reveals that it is becoming
OL,10,Fincreasingly difficult for struggling
OL,11,Ffamilies to afford and access a
OL,12,Fhealthy diet, despite promises from
OL,13,Fthe Government to create the
OL,14,Fhealthiest generation of children ever
OL,15,Fand reduce child poverty. This isn't
OL,16,Fgood enough.
OL,26,@pD@SOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
