PN,30407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781067873
OL,3,CPoorest families must spend 85% of
OL,4,Cdisposable income to get healthy diet
OL,5,C` study
OL,7,F"The Government must press ahead with
OL,8,Fits commitments made in the NHS 10-
OL,9,FYear Plan, including the mandatory
OL,10,Freporting of healthy sales by food
OL,11,Fbusinesses."
OL,13,FBarnardo's chief executive Lynn Perry
OL,14,Fsaid: "We know parents are making
OL,15,Fmajor sacrifices to ensure their
OL,16,Fchildren can eat as well as possible
OL,17,Fwithin their budgets.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@LO]vD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
